data.name: label6.Text
data.value: You should do the health fix if you are experiencing Windows crashes, faulty shortcuts, faulty system files, faulty system operations, Windows Update not working properly, no new updates, blue screens. Even if you don't experience them, we recommend running it every few months.

data.name: label13.Text
data.value: If you intend to mod OpenCleaner and sell it, please don't. We made OpenCleaner for everyone to use it the way they want and for people like you to add innovations. If you are going to make a new program using some or all of OpenCleaner's code and distribute or sell it in any way, please contact us before doing so.

data.name: label14.Text
data.value: If you've modded OpenCleaner and added new themes or features for example, please contact us and we'll share it with everyone. In this way, everyone can see your talent and keep your computer clean with a clean and light program!

data.name: label21.Text
data.value: Very good question mate! The biggest difference between these 2 cleaning programs we offer you is that OpenCleaner is open source. In this way, anyone can contribute to the program. On the other hand, YCleaner is only produced by us (YagiSoft). While YCleaner has more features, much better interface, antivirus feature, advanced tools, advanced settings, OpenCleaner does not. OpenCleaner is mostly for people who already know how to use the computer but have difficulties in cleaning and looking for an easy method, and especially for other software developers.

data.name: label19.Text
data.value: We do work, play games or have fun on our computers every day. Every time we install and delete a program, unnecessary files remain on our computer. Although there are various methods of cleaning them, including inside Windows, unfortunately they do not work at full performance and therefore sometimes GBs of garbage files can remain on our computer. Apart from that, sometimes Windows can get corrupted and fixing it can be a complete torture. Using the tools is unfortunately not as good after Windows 10 as it used to be. Here we put all of these features and more in YCleaner and OpenCleaner. With these 2 programs we offer you, we aim to solve all these problems and ensure that you get full performance from your computer!
